====Adjective====
'''A1''' or '''A-1'''
# In good health. Derived from "A-1 at Lloyd's", an old marine insurance phrase, referring to [[Wikipedia:Lloyd's of London|Lloyd's of London]] insurance company registering first-class ships as ''A-1''.

